@startuml
autonumber

title "System Sequence Diagram - US01 : Create a Map"

actor "Editor" as Editor
participant ":System" as System

activate Editor
Editor -> System: asks to create a new map

activate System
System --> Editor: requests map data (name, width, height)
deactivate System

Editor -> System: inputs requested data
activate System

note right of System
  Acceptance Criteria:
  - Map dimensions must be positive integers
  - Map name must be a valid filename
end note
System --> Editor: shows map data and requests confirmation
deactivate
Editor -> System: confirms data

activate System
System --> Editor: displays operation success
System --> Editor: displays map details
deactivate System
@enduml